    <h1>Middle of Funnel (MOFU)</h1>
    <p class="description">The consideration stage of the buyer journey where prospects know their problem and are actively comparing solutions. <strong>MOFU is where deals are won or lost</strong> — before a salesperson ever gets involved.</p>
